  "detailed_description": "A minimalistic 2d puzzle platformer exploring the ideas of playing with light and shadow to manipulate the world around you to continue. Progress through a series of levels providing new and unique challenges all based around what exists in the light, versus what exists in the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/5525c7453d1b7424a9795c4138dcbe1c.poster.avif?t=1722353555\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/5525c7453d1b7424a9795c4138dcbe1c.webm?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/5525c7453d1b7424a9795c4138dcbe1c.mp4?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Luminus comes packed will a full fledged in-game level editor. This same editor is used to create all of the existing packaged levels included with the game, giving you the same power to make levels in any way you see fit. Publish your levels to the Steam workshop, and try the levels from other people.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/2e4f4b6085f430d6f8c37d4d66b84ab4.poster.avif?t=1722353555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/2e4f4b6085f430d6f8c37d4d66b84ab4.webm?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/2e4f4b6085f430d6f8c37d4d66b84ab4.mp4?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A minimalistic 2d puzzle platformer exploring the ideas of playing with light and shadow to manipulate the world around you to continue. Progress through a series of levels providing new and unique challenges all based around what exists in the light, versus what exists in the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/5525c7453d1b7424a9795c4138dcbe1c.poster.avif?t=1722353555\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/5525c7453d1b7424a9795c4138dcbe1c.webm?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/5525c7453d1b7424a9795c4138dcbe1c.mp4?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Luminus comes packed will a full fledged in-game level editor. This same editor is used to create all of the existing packaged levels included with the game, giving you the same power to make levels in any way you see fit. Publish your levels to the Steam workshop, and try the levels from other people.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/2e4f4b6085f430d6f8c37d4d66b84ab4.poster.avif?t=1722353555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/2e4f4b6085f430d6f8c37d4d66b84ab4.webm?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681590/extras/2e4f4b6085f430d6f8c37d4d66b84ab4.mp4?t=1722353555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
